From f778ba28e43ce9adb0d62c1d8dc9605b24731ac3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ripan Deuri <rdeuri@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Jun 2025 16:15:04 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: DP: wifi: ath12k: Advertise TX_QUEUE mac hw flag

To avoid tx queuing in mac80211, advertise TX_QUEUE mac hw flag
which enable tx queuing in driver and avoid performance degradation.

Signed-off-by: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Ripan Deuri <rdeuri@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
index be50fca..3f50111 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
@@ -17541,6 +17541,7 @@ static int ath12k_mac_hw_register(struct ath12k_hw *ah)
 	ieee80211_hw_set(hw, NO_VIRTUAL_MONITOR);
 	ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORT_ECM_REGISTRATION);
 	ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_TID_CLASS_OFFLOAD);
+	ieee80211_hw_set(hw, HAS_TX_QUEUE);
 
 	if (ath12k_frame_mode == ATH12K_HW_TXRX_ETHERNET) {
 		ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_TX_ENCAP_OFFLOAD);
-- 
2.34.1

